\cf2 AT+CPIN="xxxx"\cf4  \cf3 replace xxxx by your PINCODE. should return OK. you have access to the SIM\cf4 \
\cf2 AT+CLCK="SC",0,"xxxx"\cf5  \cf3 replace xxxx by your PINCODE. disable pin code
\f1\b \cf0 \
